channel.title: On my dedicated server it says server is in use when i auto restart!
channel.description:
Alright. Well I have been having this error when I auto restart my server. It says Server is in use. Please tell me how to fix this. AND NO I DO NOT HAVE ANOTHER RUNNING SERVER ON THE SAME PORT.
Thank you.
